{"tid":2318782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隊名去商業化 廣州富力傳欲改稱廣州藍獅 因粵語諧音具貶義被否決","createTime":"2020-12-09T14:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T20:30:31.000Z","uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"105f162875687748d1ca8d449441fe19e453f255","tid":2318782,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20201209/s00006/c4c8d1b7e8b98cbb7fd41915278c5f09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20201209%2Fs00006%2Fc4c8d1b7e8b98cbb7fd41915278c5f09.jpg&h=2cc7ccde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，中國足協為求球壇去商業化，下令各球隊來季設工資帽及需改「中性名稱」，新名字不能與企業相關。中超勁旅廣州恒大已率先易名為廣州隊，同市的廣州富力有傳想新季改稱廣州藍獅，但因藍獅粤語諧音有貶義，建議或被否決，令球隊最終命名為廣州城。<br />\n<br />\n由於廣州富力會徽有兩隻藍色獅子，因此上周開始傳出易名為廣州藍獅。然而廣州《信息時報》指，提議受到不少反對聲音，因為中國足壇曾經出現廈門藍獅隊，藍獅兩字「在粤語方言中亦有着貶義的意味」，最終可能易名為廣州城或廣州五羊。廣州富力在1986年以瀋陽足球隊的名義創立，前身亦包括華晨汽車、瀋陽金德等前中甲球會，於2011年落戶廣州並獲富力集團入主。<br />\n<br />\n根據陸媒公開的中國足協「中性名稱」要求框架，今季中超16隊或只得大連人的隊名符合新規定，北京國安、上海申花等最少5隊已在本周初發聯合聲明，批評一刀切做法損害足球文化傳承。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20201209/s00006/1607506171600/%e4%b8%ad%e8%b6%85-%e9%9a%8a%e5%90%8d%e5%8e%bb%e5%95%86%e6%a5%ad%e5%8c%96-%e5%bb%a3%e5%b7%9e%e5%af%8c%e5%8a%9b%e5%82%b3%e6%ac%b2%e6%94%b9%e7%a8%b1%e5%bb%a3%e5%b7%9e%e8%97%8d%e7%8d%85-%e5%9b%a0%e7%b2%b5%e8%aa%9e%e8%ab%a7%e9%9f%b3%e5%85%b7%e8%b2%b6%e7%be%a9%e8%a2%ab%e5%90%a6%e6%b1%ba?fbclid=IwAR3itZTf5oSa9igg9bi7KTRAvQvwMlcLV4KCXfhLVG467QLz9HxiQa6FzK0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20201209%2Fs00006%2F1607506171600%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e8%25b6%2585-%25e9%259a%258a%25e5%2590%258d%25e5%258e%25bb%25e5%2595%2586%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e5%258c%2596-%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%25b7%259e%25e5%25af%258c%25e5%258a%259b%25e5%2582%25b3%25e6%25ac%25b2%25e6%2594%25b9%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%25b7%259e%25e8%2597%258d%25e7%258d%2585-%25e5%259b%25a0%25e7%25b2%25b5%25e8%25aa%259e%25e8%25ab%25a7%25e9%259f%25b3%25e5%2585%25b7%25e8%25b2%25b6%25e7%25be%25a9%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e5%2590%25a6%25e6%25b1%25ba%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3itZTf5oSa9igg9bi7KTRAvQvwMlcLV4KCXfhLVG467QLz9HxiQa6FzK0&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=ec5bdae4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e9%25ab%2594%25e8%2582%25b2%2Farticle%2F20201209%2Fs00006%2F1607506171600%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e8%25b6%2585-%25e9%259a%258a%25e5%2590%258d%25e5%258e%25bb%25e5%2595%2586%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e5%258c%2596-%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%25b7%259e%25e5%25af%258c%25e5%258a%259b%25e5%2582%25b3%25e6%25ac%25b2%25e6%2594%25b9%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e5%25bb%25a3%25e5%25b7%259e%25e8%2597%258d%25e7%258d%2585-%25e5%259b%25a0%25e7%25b2%25b5%25e8%25aa%259e%25e8%25ab%25a7%25e9%259f%25b3%25e5%2585%25b7%25e8%25b2%25b6%25e7%25be%25a9%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e5%2590%25a6%25e6%25b1%25ba%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3itZTf5oSa9igg9bi7KTRAvQvwMlcLV4KCXfhLVG467QLz9HxiQa6FzK0&h=96015df0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e9%ab%94%e8%82%b2/article/20201209/s00006/1607506171600/%e4%b8%ad%e8%b6%85-%e9%9a%8a%e5%90%8d%e5%8e%bb%e5%95%86%e6%a5%ad%e5%8c%96-%e5%bb%a3%e5%b7%9e%e5%af%8c%e5%8a%9b%e5%82%b3%e6%ac%b2%e6%94%b9%e7%a8%b1%e5%bb%a3%e5%b7%9e%e8%97%8d%e7%8d%85-%e5%9b%a0%e7%b2%b5%e8%aa%9e%e8%ab%a7%e9%9f%b3%e5%85%b7%e8%b2%b6%e7%be%a9%e8%a2%ab%e5%90%a6%e6%b1%ba?fbclid=IwAR3itZTf5oSa9igg9bi7KTRAvQvwMlcLV4KCXfhLVG467QLz9HxiQa6FzK0</a>"},{"pid":"fa34bf007a6bf1e429a8e1a3c7a2425ea397dafc","tid":2318782,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:09:04.000Z","msg":"講咗廿幾年廣東話唔知貶個位係邊"},{"pid":"fc7a20fa8ec6e65032638133552a68b45dd609fe","tid":2318782,"uid":686,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa34bf007a6bf1e429a8e1a3c7a2425ea397dafc","tid":2318782,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:09:04.000Z","msg":"講咗廿幾年廣東話唔知貶個位係邊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T15:33